  <entry>
    <title>oracle建表和基本操作</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/09/27/oracle%E5%BB%BA%E8%A1%A8%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/09/27/oracle%E5%BB%BA%E8%A1%A8%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C/</id>
    <published>2022-09-27T05:20:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-30T03:15:21.674Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/hint.css/2.4.1/hint.min.css"><h3 id="数据库基本操作"><a href="#数据库基本操作" class="headerlink" title="数据库基本操作"></a>数据库基本操作</h3><h4 id="1-Oracle基本命令"><a href="#1-Oracle基本命令" class="headerlink" title="1. Oracle基本命令"></a>1. Oracle基本命令</h4><p>以管理员身份登录sql</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlpuls <span class="operator">/</span>nolog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连接数据库</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conn <span class="operator">/</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> sysdba</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建用户user6374 ，密码user6374   </p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> <span class="keyword">user</span>  user6374 identified <span class="keyword">by</span> user6374 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查询数据字典</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_name <span class="keyword">from</span> dba_tables</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> dba_users</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查询user6374 </p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> username  <span class="keyword">from</span> dba_users</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>给user0923授权,赋予connect,resource 两个角色</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">grant</span> <span class="keyword">connect</span>,resource <span class="keyword">to</span> user6374 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以user6374帐号登陆</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conn user6374<span class="operator">/</span>user6374   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>展示用户</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">show</span> <span class="keyword">user</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建表</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> <span class="keyword">table</span> tbl_student(</span><br><span class="line"> stu_id <span class="type">int</span> <span class="keyword">primary</span> key,</span><br><span class="line"> stu_name varchar2(<span class="number">30</span>) <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>,</span><br><span class="line"> stu_sex <span class="type">char</span>(<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="string">&#x27;m&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line"> stu_birth <span class="type">date</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">null</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看表结构</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> tbl_student</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看用户创建的表的信息的数据字典</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> user_tables</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看user_tables 确认表的存在</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> table_name <span class="keyword">from</span> user_tables</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="operator">*</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> user_tables</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看user_constraints确认约束的存在</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> user_constraints <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>约束表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> owner table_name,constraint_name.constraint_type <span class="keyword">from</span> user_constraints<span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>查询本表约束</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="operator">*</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> user_constraints<span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>查询约束条数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><ul><li>增删改查实践</li></ul><p>创建一个序列</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> sequence seq_stu_id</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 显示用户序列表</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> user_sequences</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示序列<br> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> sequence_name,min_value,max_value <span class="keyword">from</span> user_sequences</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>插入一条数据</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">insert into tbl_student values(seq_stu_id.nextval,&#x27;mary&#x27;,default,sysdate)//id为2，姓名marry，生日为系统时间</span><br><span class="line">insert into tbl_student values(seq_stu_id.nextval,&#x27;mike&#x27;,&#x27;m&#x27;,to_date(&#x27;2002-10-29&#x27;),&#x27;yyyy-mm-dd&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查询表</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> tbl_student</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> stu_id,stu_name <span class="keyword">from</span> tbl_student</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改表</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> tbl_student <span class="keyword">set</span> stu_name<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;tom&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">where</span> stu_id<span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">2</span> <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>修改marry的名字为tom</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> tbl_student <span class="keyword">set</span> stu_name<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;john&#x27;</span>,stu_sex<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;f&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">where</span> stu_id<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;3&#x27;</span><span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>修改id为<span class="number">3</span>的人姓名性别</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>删除记录</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> tbl_student <span class="keyword">where</span> stu_id<span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">2</span> <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>删除id为<span class="number">2</span>的数据</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> tbl_student <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>全删除</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> <span class="keyword">table</span> tbl_student<span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>删除表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>退出系统，删除用户</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exit <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>退出</span><br><span class="line">conn <span class="operator">/</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> sysdba <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>以管理员身登录</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> <span class="keyword">user</span> user6374 cascade <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>删除用户及所有内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-Sqlplus"><a href="#2-Sqlplus" class="headerlink" title="2. Sqlplus"></a>2. Sqlplus</h4><p>建用户名和密码oracle ,oracle </p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> <span class="keyword">user</span> username identified <span class="keyword">by</span> password</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>授权 grant connect,resource,dba,sysdba to username; </p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">grant</span> <span class="keyword">connect</span>,resource,dba <span class="keyword">to</span> username</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">connect</span> username<span class="operator">/</span>password</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示PLsql输出结果</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> serveroutput <span class="keyword">on</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
